# Local dev: leave VITE_API_URL unset so requests go to the same origin as Vite
# (http://localhost:5173) and the dev server proxies /api and /socket.io to the backend.
# This avoids browser "Network Error" from CORS or localhost/IPv6 mismatches.
#
# If you prefer the browser to call the API directly, uncomment:
# VITE_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:5001
